Season: 1929

Argentina, November 1-17. All games played in Buenos Aires. The 1928 edition was suspended due to the participation of Uruguay and Argentina in the Olympic Games in Amsterdam, where they won gold and silver, respectively. Brazil, Bolivia and Chile withdrew.

